'''Giovanni Sommaripa''' (died 1468) was the lord of [[Andros]] island from 1466 until his death in battle against the [[Ottoman Empire|Ottomans]] in 1468.{{sfn|Miller|1908|p=611}}{{sfn|Setton|1978|p=292}} He was a son of [[Domenico Sommaripa]]. He was succeeded by his brother, [[Crusino II Sommaripa]].

